channel.title: New RSPS RotateX ~Awesome server~
channel.description:
Hello great Community this is sakoo99 bringing you an awesome RSPS called RotateX!!
Before You Continue Ready, the pictures are in the dropbox link! Not a download, just an album :)
Some great features:
~General Features~ -ECO and Pking system to suit all players -New Home & New Zones with great drops -Custom Icons ingame -Custom Rooms and Zones -Npc Kill Shop -Pk Point Shop -Amazing Donator zone with loads of shops! -So many commands with npc drop commands example ::npcdrops -Custom weens - scrafs - rainbow phats - wings ~250+ customs~ -All levels go to 125 -No lag, on a vps -Nex and a lot of bosses! -God Wars! -All skills working 100% -All ladders working 100% -Great donator features, new drops, weapons, donor only armour!! :D -Fixed all dupes -So much unique stuff that makes us different, come and checkout!! :) -We brought back the good ol' c key zones and all that for more fun :)
Pictures: THE ALBUM IS IN THE DROPBOX LINK :D : [url=https://www.dropbox.com/sh/j6xh7tve3h92nb0/AAAxUTyncss1SL3DxGWrTGAEa?dl=0]https://www.dropbox.com/sh/j6xh7tve3h92nb0/AAAxUTyncss1SL3DxGWrTGAEa?dl=0 [/url] Link for the server: http://rotatexrsps.com/
Thanks and that's it for me ! Hope To see you in-game :)
